<html>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#222; line-height:1.5; font-size:14px;">
    <p>Dear {!Manager},</p>

    <p>
This is to bring to your attention that the Temporary Channel Partner <strong>{!Broker__c.Name}</strong>, created by {!Broker__c.CreatedBy}, has not been registered even after 15 days of creation.
    </p>

    <p>
      Request you to kindly look into this matter and take necessary action to ensure timely registration, to avoid delays in payment processing.
    </p>

      <p>Click on link to apply for registration :-</p>
<a href="{!$Label.Site_Url_New}/channelpartner/s/customregisterpage?tempcpid={!Broker__c.RW_Broker_Number__c}">Portal Onboarding Link <a/></p>


    <p style="margin-top:24px;">
      Regards<br/>
      <strong>Runwal Enterprises</strong>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>